Thank you 'IceBane' for uploading this Family Guy Star Wars Trilogy!
Audio and video quality is very good! (But who needs 1080p full-HD for a simple "old school" cartoon?)
All three movies have the original English audio. However - as mentioned in the "small print" - not all movies have (English, Swedish, Norwegian, Danish, Spanish and Dutch) subtitles.

The torrent only includes English subtitles for the first 2 episodes, but I found a DVD rip subtitle that syncs with "It's A Trap":

http://subscene.com/english/Family-Guy-Presents-Its-a-Trap/subtitle-395312.aspx
